Using social media for your business is easy, but many businesses don't actually use it to their advantage. Facebook is not a bullhorn. It is a place for building engaged communities around problem and solutions that your business and your customers deal with. Instagram is a place for sharing inspirations, successes and motivational images. Twitter is a casual conversation network. LinkedIn is for growing your business presence within an industry.

If you're using the same content on each platform 100% of the time, you're not putting forth the right amount of effort to utilize these platforms to maximize their potential.
